**Wire** (new): Arbor iterates all plugins and collects every `supportKit` entry into a central `ContributionRegistry`. Fires `phase:wired` when complete. No apparatus `start()` has been called yet.

**Start** (refined): Each apparatus runs `start()` in dependency order. Contributions are already fully available via `ctx.contributions()`. Fires `phase:started` when all apparatuses have completed `start()`.

