// After:
for (const entry of ctx.contributions<AnyTool[]>('tools')) {
  for (const tool of entry.value) {
    this.registerTool(entry.pluginId, tool);
  }
}
```

Same pattern for Fabricator (engines), Loom (roles), Spider (rig templates, block types, engines), Clerk (writ types).

