Keep it, but clarify its purpose. It is NOT for contribution discovery (that's the Wire phase). It's for apparatus-to-apparatus notifications where one apparatus needs to react to another apparatus completing `start()` — e.g., registering CDC watchers on another apparatus's Stacks books.

